Title: KUBE: New workload resource: DaemonSets
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1646223408
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.2.0b1

This werk introduces DaemonSets to the Kubernetes agent. Similar to the
other Kubernetes objects, Checkmk creates a piggyback host for each
DaemonSet. A DaemonSet host supports

- Pod resources
- Memory resources
- CPU resources
- Info
- HW/SW inventory
